<!-- About activity -->
    <string name="title_about">About</string>
    <string name="aboutText">
        Here is a small multi-user currency converter application.\n
        It supports user authorization through simple google account as well as google+ social networking.\n
        Also, guest-mode session is allowed.\n
        Conversion for 168 world currencies is executed both in online- and offline-mode (last remembered exchange rates are used).\n
        List of current exchange operations is stored and can be reviewed next time.
    </string>

